{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/Gif_1.gif?t=1737678342\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endure the harsh depths of Lightwood</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your destiny awaits for you! Discover the ancient mysteries behind the Kingdom's </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">decay as you meet all kinds of interesting insects and deadly foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/Gif_2.gif?t=1737678342\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore an ancient fallen kingdom inside a dying tree</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the wonderful and hunting insect kingdom awaiting for you in the </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">depths of Lightwood. There are secrets and mysteries behind every corner waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/Gif_3.gif?t=1737678342\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master your skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every new area will be filled with multiple dangers to overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Knowledge over you skills will be key to progression and survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/Gif_4.gif?t=1737678342\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A semi-open world Metroidvania</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of Lightwood is meant to be explored however you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">want, but you will have to earn that right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Well balanced and responsive combat made to provide a fluid experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A new approach to the classical Metroidvania progression system.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A huge variety of enemies and bosses carefully created.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautifully crafted landscapes and music, made to enhance the overall game experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple purpose mechanics conceived to increase the player sense of mastery over the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join our Community</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow us on social media and discord to get more updates about the game!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737678342","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/page.bg.jpg?t=1737678342","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/3f6ab6edbd613957009e790b1060af9a133863dd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737678342","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/3f6ab6edbd613957009e790b1060af9a133863dd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737678342","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195360/extras/Gif_1.gif?t=1737678342\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endure the harsh depths of Lightwood</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your destiny awaits for you! Discover the ancient mysteries behind the Kingdom's </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">decay as you meet all kinds of interesting insects and deadly foes.</p>